formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
> In certain units aggrements to sale has not been made by the firm.					
> As per information and explanation given to me by the partners of the firm, There are total 28 parking space out of which 3 are open parking and 25 are covered parking and all parkings are to be considered as common parking. The firm is not selling parking specifically to any member.					
> In Respect of Unsecured loans taken for the project, the amount of Rs. 7,00,000/- have been repaid to Nandlal Patel in October-2020 but it has been wrongly debited to account of Harish Jayantibhai Kunpara by mistake and hence while filing of Form-3 for Period ended up to December-2020 the balance of Nandlal Patel has been wrongly shown in the list of Unsecured loan parties which have been corrected now and the loan of Nandlal Patel is totally paid of and account balance of Harish Jayantibhai Kunpara has now been correctly shown at Rs. 8,00,000/-.					
> Whenever required necessary changes have been made according to information and explanation have been provided to me by the partners of the firm.
